    <description>Replaces 5 Workflow Rules:
- Contract - Record Type Changes - DELIVERY
- Contract - Record Type Changes - EVENT
- Contract - Record Type Changes to Unlocked - DELIVERY
- Contract - Record Type Changes to Unlocked - EVENT
- Contract: Status Field Update from Activated to Active

Purpose:
- Automatically locks/unlocks Contract Record Types based on Status transitions.
- Update Status from &quot;Activated&quot; to &quot;Active&quot; for Rec Types: Delivery Contract, Billing - Internal Only, or Billing - Cancel/Refund, 

Impacted Record Types (RecordTypeId):
- Delivery_Contract (01214000000AV7yAAG)
- Delivery_Contract_Locked (01214000001RYWeAAO)
- Billing - Internal Only (01214000000AVmNAAW)
- Billing - Cancel/Refund (01214000000AVoOAAW)
- Event_Contract (012a0000001RKA9AAO)
- Event_Contract_Locked (01214000001RYWjAAO)

Primary Actions:
- Convert to Locked when in Approved/Updated/Canceled/Activated
- Convert to Unlocked when transitioned back to Active/Rejected/Editing/Re-Submit
- Normalize Activated status to Active</description>
